## Summary

This room covers the fundamentals of a Security Operations Center (SOC) — the dedicated team responsible for monitoring, detecting, and responding to security threats 24/7. The practical exercise involved acting as a Level 1 SOC Analyst, investigating a port scanning alert in a SIEM solution using the 5 Ws framework.

## Tools Used

- SIEM (Security Information and Event Management) — log analysis and alert investigation

