### The 5 Ws of Alert Triage

| W | Question | Example |
|---|----------|---------|
| **What?** | What happened? | Port scanning / malware detected |
| **When?** | When did it happen? | June 12, 2024 17:24 |
| **Where?** | Where did it happen? | Destination IP 10.0.0.3 |
| **Who?** | Who is responsible? | Source host NESSUS |
| **Why?** | Why did it happen? | Intended / Malicious |

